<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <title>禮貌小先鋒 - Manner Squad</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0; padding: 0;
            background-color: #f0f8ff;
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'PingFang HK', 'Microsoft JhengHei', Arial, sans-serif;
            display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh; overflow: hidden; touch-action: manipulation;
        }
        #gameApp {
            width: 100%; max-width: 960px; aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
            background: #ffffff; border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            position: relative; display: flex; flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center; justify-content: space-between;
            box-sizing: border-box; padding: 3vh 4vw;
        }
        @media (max-aspect-ratio: 16/9) {
            #gameApp { width: 95vw; height: calc(95vw * 9 / 16); }
        }
        #debugLog {
            position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; 
            background: rgba(220, 53, 69, 0.9); color: white;
            font-size: 1.8vh; padding: 0.5vh 1vw; z-index: 999;
            box-sizing: border-box; display: none; text-align: center;
        }
        .screen { display: none; width: 100%; height: 100%; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; }
        .screen.active { display: flex; }
        h1 { color: #2B8A3E; font-size: 4.5vh; margin: 0 0 1vh 0; }
        p { color: #495057; font-size: 2.5vh; margin: 0 0 3vh 0; text-align: center; }
        .score-bar { align-self: flex-start; font-size: 2.6vh; font-weight: bold; color: #495057; margin-bottom: 0.5vh; }
        .scenario-container {
            background: #f8f9fa; border: 3px solid #dee2e6; border-radius: 16px;
            width: 90%; padding: 2vh 2vw; text-align: center;
            display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center;
        }
        .scenario-emoji { font-size: 6vh; margin-bottom: 0.5vh; line-height: 1; }
        .scenario-text { font-size: 2.8vh; font-weight: bold; color: #212529; line-height: 1.3; }
        .audio-control-deck { margin-top: 1.5vh; }
        .audio-btn-whole {
            background: #E6FFFA; border: 2px solid #0EA5E9; border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1vh 2.5vw; color: #0EA5E9; font-weight: bold; font-size: 2vh;
            cursor: pointer; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5vw;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }
        .choices-grid { display: flex; justify-content: center; gap: 3vw; width: 100%; margin-top: 1vh; }
        .choice-wrapper { flex: 1; max-width: 240px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 1vh; }
        .choice-card {
            border-radius: 16px; width: 100%; height: 16vh;
            display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            cursor: pointer; box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        .choice-icon { font-size: 4vh; margin-bottom: 0.2vh; }
        .choice-text { font-size: 3.5vh; font-weight: bold; color: #ffffff; text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.15); }
        .speaker-bubble-outside {
            background: #f1f3f5; border: 2px solid #ced4da; border-radius: 50%;
            width: 5vh; height: 5vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            font-size: 2.5vh; color: #495057; cursor: pointer; box-shadow: 0 3px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        }
        .btn-prime {
            background: #10B981; color: white; border: none; padding: 2vh 5vw;
            font-size: 3vh; font-weight: bold; border-radius: 50px; cursor: pointer;
        }
        .feedback-overlay {
            display: none; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 100%; height: 100%;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.94); border-radius: 20px;
            flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; z-index: 10;
        }
        .feedback-text { font-size: 4.5vh; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 2vh; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div id="gameApp">
    <div id="debugLog"></div>

    <div id="startScreen" class="screen active">
        <h1>禮貌小先鋒! 🚀</h1>
        <p>睇下發生咩事，幫小朋友揀個有禮貌嘅回應啦！</p>
        <button class="btn-prime" onclick="startGame()">開始遊戲</button>
    </div>

    <div id="playScreen" class="screen">
        <div class="score-bar" id="scoreDisplay">🌟 得分: 0 / 5</div>
        <div class="scenario-container">
            <div class="scenario-emoji" id="scenEmoji">🏫</div>
            <div class="scenario-text" id="scenText">載入中...</div>
            <div class="audio-control-deck">
                <button class="audio-btn-whole" onclick="playAudioFile(currentItem.audioFile)">📢 聽完整句子</button>
            </div>
        </div>
